<v-snackbar
        v-model="snackbar"
        :bottom="y === 'bottom'"
        :color="color"
        :left="x === 'left'"
        :multi-line="mode === 'multi-line'"
        :right="x === 'right'"
        :timeout="timeout"
        :top="y === 'top'"
        :vertical="mode === 'vertical'"

        class="snackbar"
    >
        {{ textoSnackbar }}
        <v-btn
            dark
            text
            icon
            @click="snackbar = false"
        >
            <v-icon
                class="mr-2"
                @click="$emit('closeSnackbar')"
            >mdi-close</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
</v-snackbar>
